The Story So Far
Since the beginning of time the universe as we know it has been transforming and new multi dimensional bridge is starting to form linking humanity to the meta verse. This bridge is a magical place where gaming meet reality.

Defi Games
Riddle as a service

We are activly looking to form partnerships with other projets providing our riddle as a service 'RAAS' partnership program.



Play To Earn

Once you've entered our games you will be rewarded for your time and effort.



Interactive Games

Gaming and explorer enjoyment is at the core of our treasure hunt product.

Farming, Staking and Treasure Vaults

We have created Treasure Valuts (Prize fund) which increases in size as more explorers participate in games. This locks BLOX until the prize is won! We also provide liquidity rewards with our official partner cafeswap where you can earn BLOX and Brew for staking or farming.
